      "content": "it's not just being tired. it's like i've failed the only thing i was ever good at. everyone saw it happen. the person they loved, the one who had it all together... that person is dead. i'm just looking at the wreckage of who i used to be and it doesn't feel like there's any point in trying to rebuild when the foundation is gone.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
